<div class="panel name-thingsshouldknowmodule">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<h3>Things you should know</h3>
<p>General surgery<br/>General surgery focuses on operation for the abdomon, including but not exclusively on the intestines, colon, liver, thyroid gland, bile duct and hernias. <br/>In the last few years minimally invasive surgery has become more prevalent such as key hole surgery to minimise the risks of infection, recovery times and also scarring.<br/><br/>General surgery also has a responsibility for breast care, including the surgical treatment of breast cancer and its sub-specialty of Mastology (breast disease).<br/><br/>The full range of diagnostic assessment and treatment services are provided.  These include: <br/>Breast Services <br/>Colorectal Services (bowel problems) <br/>Upper Gastro-Intestinal Services and Liver Services (stomach, pancreas, liver, gall bladder, etc) <br/>Vascular Services, (blood vessel problems) <br/>Paediatric Services (surgical problems in children)<br/><br/>Service Delivery <br/>Inpatient Elective (planned) - Royal Blackburn Hospital and Burnley General Hospital <br/>Inpatient Emergency (Unplanned- Royal Blackburn Hospital and Burnley General Hospital <br/>Day Case (Same Day Service) - Royal Blackburn Hospital, Burnley General Hospital and Rossendale Hospital <br/>Outpatients - Accrington Victoria Hospital, Royal Blackburn Hospital, Burnley General Hospital, Pendle Community Hospital and Rossendale Hospital <br/>Diagnostic - Royal Blackburn Hospital and Burnley General Hospital<br/><br/>Contact Details:  <br/>Switchboard - Royal Blackburn Hospital - 01254 263555<br/>Switchboard - Burnley General Hospital - 01282 425071<br/>General Surgery Outpatients Reception (Burnley)  - 01282 804058 / 804000 / 804204<br/>General Surgery Outpatients Reception (Blackburn) - 01254 734522<br/>General Surgery New Appointments - 01282 803762<br/>General Surgery Outpatients Appointments (follow up) (Blackburn) - 01254 734522<br/>General Surgery Elective Admissions - 01282 804893<br/>General Surgery Elective Admissions - 01254 734378 / 01254 734520</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
